text: Twitter Goes To Town Imagining The #ReasonsTrumpHangsUp "He doesn't speak Australian." 02/02/2017 06:40 am ET Lee Moran Trends Editor, The Huffington Post According to a report published in The Washington Post, Donald Trump prematurely ended his telephone call with Australian Prime Minister Malcolm Turnbull over the weekend, and people want to know why. Using the #ReasonsTrumpHangsUp hashtag, Twitter users speculated about the possible reasons the call may have turned sour.
